Package: PACE
Title: Predictive Adjusted Capped Estimator for Time Series Forecasting
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Vinodhkumar", "Gunasekaran", email="vinoalles@gmail.com", role=c("aut","cre"))
Description: PACE is a hybrid forecasting algorithm blending YoY, QoQ, and prior-period growth with volatility caps and seasonal adjustments to produce stable, interpretable forecasts for business and macro time series.
